<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَنَبَذْنَاهُمْ فِي الْيَمِّ}</span> ... فَأَلْقَيْنَاهُمْ وَأَغْرَقْنَاهُمْ فيِ البَحْرِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
